Package Point3D

Class Point3D

java.lang.Object
Point3D.Point3D
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Point3D.Double, Point3D.Float
public abstract class Point3D
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
The Class Point3D represents a point whose data is given in high-precision values appropriate for graphical operations.
